<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><author>John Laudon</author>
<hymn_number>22</hymn_number>
<lyrics>[V1]
 Isroilning Xudosi U dunyoning Shohi
 Xudoning qoʻzisi Iso oʻldi men uchun Rabbim
 Men tiz choʻkaman, boshimni egaman
 Sen Rabbimsan, yolgʻiz Xudoim!
 Men tiz choʻkaman, boshimni egaman
 Sen loyiqsan shohlar Shohi!</lyrics>
<title>Isroilning Xudosi U dunyoning Shohi! ҲС22</title>
</song>